name: LIFE IN DARK by Manoj Singh

metadata.name: APE OF JAIPUR
metadata.description: Galtaji Temple in Jaipur is reputed to have huge number of monkeys residing within its complex. I took this picture when I visited the temples,  many monkeys were playing around with their families, and on another side I found a single siting monkey in the corner of temple stable giving no expression, so I decided this would be the first photo of the series.
